# Best practices for using DaisyUI components

- Follow DaisyUI's theming system for consistent UI across your application
- Use DaisyUI's pre-built components to speed up development
- Customize DaisyUI components using Tailwind utility classes
- Ensure accessibility by using DaisyUI's built-in ARIA attributes
- Keep your UI components modular and reusable
